You can export a package which allows you to save it on your file-system. To export a package right-click the package and select Export. thinkParity will create a folder for you and save it to your local file system. The folder contains all versions of the package and a pdf-format summary of the history of the package.  This folder will be located in your 'My Documents\thinkParity' directory and the name will correspond to the name of the package.